Plodopitomnik () is a rural locality (a selo) in Ullubiyevsky Selsoviet, Tarumovsky District, Republic of Dagestan, Russia. Population:  There are 3 streets.
Geography
Plodopitomnik is located 24&nbsp;km southeast of Tarumovka (the district's administrative centre) by road. Aybatkhanovskoye lesnichestvo is the nearest rural locality.
